# .mailmap — canonicalize commit author/co-author identities for git log,
# git shortlog, and GitHub's Contributors tab.
#
# Format: <Canonical Name> <canonical@email>  <Old Name> <old@email>
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap

# Map AI assistants used during this work to the project owner so the
# Contributors tab shows only the human author. The actual AI assistance
# is disclosed in the README under "AI Assistance Disclosure" and in
# individual commit bodies via Co-authored-by trailers (which remain).

